== Introduction ==
To Start off here are a few examples of simple ASL sentences:

;Hello, my name is Mike.
:{{gloss|hi my name}} {{spell|mike}}
;Nice to meet you.
:{{gloss|nice meet-you}}

;What is your name?
:{{gloss|you name what?|WH}}

;I can speak ASL a little bit.
:{{gloss|ASL some i can|nod-yes}}

;I'm sorry, I didn't understand that. Can you repeat yourself?
:{{gloss|sorry, me understand-not you. again?|YN}}

;Please spell more slowly.
:{{gloss|fingerspell slow please}}

;Where is the washroom?
:{{gloss|toilet, where?|WH}}


[[Category:American Sign Language]]
